beer.beer_description:
Kia Ora !! We have made a Hazy IPA using all New Zealand ingredients and decided to go Full Nelson in the hop department. Utilizing hops from Freestyle Hops, grown in the Nelson region. The hops used in this Hazy IPA exhibit flavours and aromas of passionfruit, lime, citrus, and candied melon. This is rounded out by a juicy, full mouth feel from large oat additions. This beer is just another great reason to love our friendly neighbours across the ditch.

Malt – Gladfield Pilsner, Munich, Wheat, Oats Hops – Rakau, Motueka, Kohia Nelson
